summaries.short: Series premiere. Jesse Gemstone receives a video from blackmailers seeking to sully his reputation.
summaries.full: Series premiere. Upon returning from a baptism marathon in China with his father Eli and brother Kelvin, Jesse Gemstone receives a video from blackmailers seeking to sully his reputation. Eli moves forward with plans to expand the Gemstone empire as he continues to mourn his late wife Aimee-Leigh.
